OL,3,CPeston: Healey's resignation is PM's
OL,4,Cworst crisis yet
OL,6,FHealey's resignation is arguably the
OL,7,Fworst crisis faced by the PM, and he
OL,8,Fhas faced a few.
OL,10,FHe is saying that Keir Starmer -
OL,11,Fencouraged by Rachel Reeves and the
OL,12,FTreasury - is jeopardising the
OL,13,Fsecurity of the nation by refusing to
OL,14,Ffund any significant increase in
OL,15,Fdefence spending between 2027 and 2030.
OL,17,FHealey says that on Monday the Defence
OL,18,FInvestment Plan was shared with him,
OL,19,Fand it would involve defence as a
OL,20,Fshare of GDP rising from 2.6% to just
OL,21,F2.68% of GDP by 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
